provide - instead of <file> to read from stdin
use -a and -r together to remove and add (rebuild) annotations in one go
-a, --add add dependency injection annotations where non-existing \
-r, --remove remove all existing dependency injection annotations \
-o write output to <file>. output is written to stdout by default \
